description:
Recapping our weekends - the SEC championship, NYC with YouTubers, Visiting Freshman Dorm Room, Finals, and More! 

Advice Column - Giving our best advice we can think of on YOUR situations that you submitted to us! We talk boys, bad roommates, break ups, long distance, moving to a new place, and more.

For a total of $60 off, that’s $20 off your first 3 HelloFresh boxes, visit https://HelloFresh.com/galsonthego60 and enter galsonthego60

Follow @galsonthegopodcast on Instagram to submit your own questions for next week’s episode, get involved, and more!
